text: An assembly which places a strong emphasis on studying The Bible and a critical analysis of the Christian faith. Fundamental in its approach, it seeks to always be in touch with the core tenets of the faith against the sway of the current social pressures of the times.
Have had a major renovation ... added a new floor recently. Now, a new building with ... new makan area, new sound system, ... etc. Got piano accompaniment during worship service these days.
Best church in town..caring Elders and true teaching. Family feeling church you can experience.
Come and worship with believers of this New Testament Church.
Best place to know about Jesus Christ.
